@startuml
!option handwritten true
skinparam handwritten true
skinparam backgroundColor #fffaf0
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 15
  Shadowing true
}

title Cancer Journey - Conceptual Sketch

rectangle "Patient\n- life status & demographics\n- comorbidities\n- visits / trials" as Patient #FDE68A
rectangle "Cancer Condition\n- asserted date\n- body site, histology, biomarkers\n- imaging / biopsy as evidence" as Condition #FACC15
rectangle "Cancer Stage\n- overall stage snapshot\n- evolves across visits" as Stage #FCD34D
rectangle "Disease Extent\n- primary / loco-regional / metastatic sites\n- defined through imaging" as Extent #FDE047
rectangle "Disease Over Time & Space\n- progression or recurrence states\n- linked to treatments and assessments" as Evolution #FADB5F
rectangle "Treatment\n- intent (curative / palliative)\n- combinations of procedures" as Treatment #F8D66D
rectangle "Treatment Response\n- measured status\n- evidence from visits" as Response #FFE066

Patient "1" -- "1..*" Condition : experiences
Condition "1" -- "1..*" Stage : has stage
Condition "1" -- "0..1" Extent : has extent
Condition "1" -- "1..*" Evolution : changes over time
Condition "1" -- "1..*" Treatment : is treated by
Treatment "0..*" -- "1..1" Response : yields
Evolution "0..*" -- "0..*" Treatment : informs / triggers
Response "0..*" -- "1" Condition : relates to

note bottom of Evolution
  Captures how the condition evolves over
  visits, imaging, and other assessments.
end note

note right of Treatment
  A treatment can be a single procedure or
  a regimen; keep the intent visible.
end note

@enduml
